content: More approvals to #PfizerBioNTech vaccine: #Singapore approves @pfizer #CovidVaccine, expects first shots by December-end.
date: Singapore approves Pfizer Covid vaccine, expects first shots by December-endSingapore PM Lee Hsien Loong said first priority will be given to those who are at greatest risk: healthcare workers and front-line personnel, as well as the elderly and vulnerable.theprint.in
